snippet.title: Funkin' Corruption: REIMAGINED | EVIL BOYFRIEND vs SENPAI DAY 1! (UPDATED)
snippet.description:
Someone new has appeared in Hating Simulator. Someone rather... strange.

Funkin' Corruption: Reimagined is based off of Phantom Fear's corruption, but with an entirely twisted storyline and new songs!
